alize Mexican cinema.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aMotion picturesxMexico. 0aMotion pictureszMexico. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh  aauteur.  abunueliana.  acabaretera.  acinema.  acultural studies.  adirector.  ael.  aensayo de un crimen.  afamily melodrama.  afilm criticism.  afilm genre.  afilm history.  afilm industry.  afilm theory.  afilm.  afilmmaking.  agran casino.  ahispanic studies.  ahispanic.  alatin america.  alatino.  alos olvidados.  aluis bunuel.  amexican cinema.  amexican film.  amexican history.  amexico.  anational identity.  anationalism.  aperformance.  aperforming arts.  apolitical film.  apolitics.  asatire.  asocial commentary.  asubida al cielo.  asurrealism.  asusana.  auna mujer sin amor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052093048340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520930483423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520930483/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles